Package: backlit
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1, libglib2.0-0, libc6
Maintainer: Faykar78 <harshamerugu78@email.com>
Description: A Beautiful Keyboard Backlight Controller for Linux
 BackLit is a modern GTK4 application to control keyboard backlight 
 brightness and colors on Clevo/TUXEDO laptops.
 Features verify:
 - 12-preset Color Wheel
 - Wave Animation
 - Brightness Control
 - Global Hotkeys
